import React from 'react'

const BrandContainer = () => {
    return (
        <Row className="my-1 justify-content-between">
            <BrandCard img={brand1} />
            <BrandCard img={brand2} />
            <BrandCard img={brand3} />
            <BrandCard img={brand2} />
            <BrandCard img={brand1} />
            <BrandCard img={brand3} />
        </Row>
    )
}

export default BrandContainer
